# Keep host artifacts out of the build context. Notably node_modules: the builder runs
# its own `npm ci` for Linux, and copying the host's macOS-native node_modules over it
# would break better-sqlite3 / node-pty at runtime.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
.git
.github
.DS_Store
*.log
.claude
.agents
design-assets
docs
